sentences.en: Some two-story dwellings have interior load bearing walls.
sentences.cn: 某些两层的住房，里面有着承重墙。

sentences.en: You can imagine water levels as high as two-story buildings within 10 minutes.
sentences.cn: 你可以想象一下，在10分钟内，水位将达到两层楼的位置。

sentences.en: It was a two-story colonial painted yellow and white located in a nice neighborhood.
sentences.cn: 房子是殖民地时期的建筑风格，有两层，用黄色和白色涂料粉刷而成。
